race.description: Jacquinot First Yearlings 2026 @ Widden Maiden Plt
race.comment: MAKHACHEV (5) unwanted in betting on debut when coming out of a strong race to run third over 1300m at Randwick Kensington behind Lancelot Du Lac. Gets the right run again and Jason Collett retains the ride. SNITZEL MISS (13) deep into her prep and can overcome the awkward draw with Grima's claim. Chased hard behind the promising Jet when a narrow second over 1300m at Warwick Farm. Sure to be strong late with just 52kg to shoulder. BOTTLES OF SHELLS (15) raced without luck from the sticky draw on debut when a plugging sixth over 1100m at Canterbury. Improver out to this trip in the bigger field. PERFORMANCE (12) bounced off her two good trials on debut with a tough on speed second over 1100m at Canterbury. Has further upside to come and must be respected despite drawing poorly.
